				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Has anyone had this happen to them in an AE kite?<a name="49109"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 29 04 4:07 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>1) You do something to screw up (You let Selo's or SoW wear off, you hit a movement key and broke your auto circle, etc).
<br />

<br />
2) You get bashed by 40 mobs, stunned, and knocked back a decent distance.
<br />

<br />
3) The mobs *don't* chase you while you're stunned and spinning.
<br />

<br />
4) Stun wears off.
<br />

<br />
5) The mobs start chasing you again.
<br />

<br />
This happened to me a few times.  I appreciated not having to hit deftdance, but it did seem kind of weird.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
