				<td colspan="2"><span>I've also noticed two types of stuns.  The aforementioned stun I don't mind because I know I'll survive, btw this happens with just run on also as I never use selos to kite.  The second stun turns me and is almost certain death.  The num lock will have me running back right into the pack or certainly on an angle they will hit me again.  And usually two hits by 30-40 mobs will do me in.  But I don't know what causes a 'spin-stun' versus a stun that just brings you to a stop with no turning whatsoever.  Anyone?</span></td>
